00:37:39,270 --> 00:37:40,450
Tady.

386
00:37:48,740 --> 00:37:49,770
To je pěkné.

387
00:37:58,440 --> 00:37:59,820
Měl bych si taky lehnout.

388
00:38:02,350 --> 00:38:03,470
Takhle je to lepší.

389
00:38:07,270 --> 00:38:11,270
